{"_id":"LlrkcfKvNsehx2IC","name":"Art of Destruction","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","flags":{"importid":"ADVnXvZV2nCJx8aV","cf":{"id":"temp_rw0bbv9j8v"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st, 5th, 9th, 13th, and 17th level,&nbsp;the magus increases the destructive scale for a number of his spells. He selects one of the following area-types each time he gains this class ability. Any time he casts a damaging area-effect spell, he gains the listed benefit. He may take the same area-type multiple times, its effects stack.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Burst:&nbsp;</em>Increase radius by 5 feet.</li>\n<li><em>Cone:&nbsp;</em>Increase cone-radius by 10 feet.</li>\n<li><em>Cylinder:&nbsp;</em>Increase radius by 5 ft and Height by 10 ft.</li>\n<li><em>Line:&nbsp;</em>Increase the lines length by 20 feet or its Width by 5 ft.</li>\n<li><em>Wall:&nbsp;</em>Increase length by 10 ft and Height by 5 ft.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces black magery.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Casting"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"artOfDestruction","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Magus"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"