{"_id":"N3ZEkTlUSO0L3AUb","name":"Black Magery","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","flags":{"importid":"7PVBxBxR507ICyRg","cf":{"id":"temp_9fkkmg2fzgf"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level and every four black mage levels thereafter, a black mage increases his power with his spells of 1st level or higher. This ability applies only to spells that he casts as a&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">black</span> mage, not to those he might have by virtue of levels in another class. At each such opportunity, he can choose from the list of the following (with a maximum of 2 per):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Elemental Mastery:</em>&nbsp;This increases the black mage&rsquo;s caster level by 1 for all spells with an elemental descriptor.</li>\n<li><em>Increased Damage:</em> This increases any damage spell from the black mage spell list the black mage casts by 1 extra die of the appropriate type. This allows you to overcome any damage cap a spell might restrict you to. Only applies once per casting, such spells with multiple attacks (such as Ruin) only applies to 1 missile.</li>\n<li><em>Spell Mastery:</em>&nbsp;This increases the DC for all of the black mage&rsquo;s spells by 1.</li>\n<li><em>Spell Penetration:</em> This increases the black mage&rsquo;s caster level checks by 1 made to overcome a creature&rsquo;s spell resistance. This stacks with the Spell Penetration feat.</li>\n</ul>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Casting"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"blackMagery","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFe