{"_id":"UENaE6Y9JV8xIqzb","name":"Mage Talents","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","flags":{"importid":"5FHA3GajKQ7zXT4q","cf":{"id":"temp_9fkkmg2fzgf"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a black mage gains experience, he learns a number of talents that assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, a black mage gains one mage talent. A black mage cannot select an individual talent more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/\">Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</h3>\n<p>At 12th, and every two levels thereafter, a black mage learns further talents to assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. He may choose one of the following advanced mage talents in place of a mage talent. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of advanced mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/#advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Black Mage Talent","Black Mage Talent, Advanced"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNote