{"_id":"aKEHuiU9muGFbj7N","name":"Mass Destruction","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","flags":{"importid":"FRscXh56UCHpEUrV","cf":{"id":"temp_rw0bbv9j8v"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, the magus gains the <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/feats/metamagic-feats/widen-spell/\">Widen Spell</a> feat. If he already possesses this feat then he chooses another metamagic or item creation feat instead. At 10th level, the MP cost of the Widen Spell metamagic feat is reduced by 1 for any area-effect spell he casts. At 15th level, increase the effects of the Widen Spell metamagic feat by +100% (base radius x3). At 20th level, the Widen Spell metamagic feat costs no additional MP for any black mage area-effect spell he casts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces metamagic enhancement.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Feat","Casting"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"massDestruction","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Magus"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":false,"prf":false,"pil":false,"pro":false,"rep":false,"rid":false,"sen":false,"slt":false,"spl":false,"ste":false,"