{"_id":"u9hhNqYBHykLOOpN","name":"Innate Spells","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","flags":{"importid":"VcnOdMwL8cmpc4bv","cf":{"id":"temp_9fkkmg2fzgf"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As the black mage&rsquo;s mastery of magic grows deeper, he learns to cast a small number of spells without spending magic points. Beginning at 6th level, a black mage may select one 1st-<wbr />level black magic spell he knows and is able to cast. He may now cast this spell once per day as a spell-<wbr />like ability without needing to spend MP. The caster level for this spell is equal to the black mage&rsquo;s caster level. At 9th level and every three levels thereafter (12th, 15th, and 18th level), the black mage may select an additional spell which he can cast once per day as a spell-<wbr />like ability. The maximum spell level which can be chosen at each of these intervals is indicated on the table below.</p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-61A\">Table: Innate Spells</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table id=\"tablepress-61A\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-61A small-width\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n<th class=\"column-1\">Level</th>\n<th class=\"column-2\">Maximum Spell Level</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">6th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">1st</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">9th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">2nd or lower</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">12th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">3rd or lower</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">15th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">4th or lower</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">18th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">5th or lower</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Spells"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":f